dot("$4 + 3i$", A, NE);
dot("$4 - 3i$", B, SE);
dot("$-4 - 3i$", C, SW);
dot("$-4 + 3i$", D, NW);
[/asy]

The area of this rectangle is $6 \cdot 8 = \boxed{48}.$

